<p>Do you find buying and cooking whole fish intimidating? Hopefully, this recipe will encourage you to get some lovely whole trout or snapper next time you&#8217;re visiting your local fishmonger. Find more <a href="https://www.cookedandloved.com/recipes/ingredients/fish-seafood/">healthy fish recipes here.</a></p>
<p>Not only this whole baked trout dish is extremely nutritious &#8211; omega-3 fatty acids, vitamin B12, minerals and protein -but it&#8217;s also very easy to make and you will have dinner ready in <a href="https://www.cookedandloved.com/recipes/type/30-minute-meals/">30 minutes</a>&#8230;.just like <a href="https://www.cookedandloved.com/20-paleo-friendly-jamie-oliver-recipes/">Jamie Oliver</a>.&nbsp;</p>
<div class="content_hint">&nbsp;</div>
